node.text:
This Hennessey Venom 1000 GT500 Mustang makes 859 rear wheel HP and 669 rear wheel lb-ft torque on our Dynojet chassis dyno using E85. This performance upgrade features a flex fuel tune that also supports 93 Octane.⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠

node.text:
Chevrolet's C7 Corvette Z06 production may be over, but the aftermarket performance upgrades are still strong! Hennessey is proud to offer reliable, blistering performance upgrades for this LT4-platformed machine. This HPE850 performance upgrade is expertly installed and calibrated, supported by world class customer service, and guaranteed with a 2 year / 24k mile warranty.

Learn more: http://hennesseyperformance.com/vehic...​

Up your Z06 to 850 (or 1000!) HP with Hennessey:
979-885-1300 | http://www.HennesseyPerformance.com

node.title: 850 HP Hennessey Corvette Z06 // SIGHTS AND SOUNDS!

🚨INTRODUCING THE 30TH ANNIVERSARY EXORCIST🚨

Since 1991, Hennessey has proudly made your fast cars faster. To celebrate our company's 30th anniversary, we are offering a commemorative series of one of our favorite performance upgrades- THE EXORCIST. This Camaro ZL1 upgrade features all the trappings of our impeccably designed and calibrated 1000 HP upgrade in addition to a special Hennessey 30th Anniversary exterior graphic, 30th Anniversary engine bay and interior plaques serial numbered 1-30, and is signed by the man himself, John Hennessey. 

Call now for more information! 979-885-1300
